    <item>
      <title>欧盟财长称，欧盟即将就交易规则延期做出决定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/eu-finance-chief-promises-decision-on-bank-capital-soon-amid-uk-and-us-delays</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟财政部长表示，随着欧洲面临越来越大的压力，要求其效仿其他地区推迟实施巴塞尔协议 III，欧盟将于近期宣布实施巴塞尔协议 III 中有关银行交易活动的部分计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/eu-finance-chief-promises-decision-on-bank-capital-soon-amid-uk-and-us-delays</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 10:13:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Adani Power 获得董事会批准通过股票出售筹集 5.78 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/adani-power-gets-board-nod-to-raise-578-million-via-share-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该公司周三表示，阿达尼电力有限公司 (Adani Power Ltd.) 计划通过向合格的机构买家出售股票筹集高达 500 亿卢比（5.78 亿美元），此举旨在加强其资本支出计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/adani-power-gets-board-nod-to-raise-578-million-via-share-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 10:10:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德表示将重点关注美国股票，并选择性投资其他领域</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-29/blackrock-focus-on-us-equities-selectivity-elsewhere-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德欧洲、中东和非洲地区投资和投资组合解决方案主管乌尔苏拉·马尔基奥尼 (Ursula Marchioni) 讨论了股市对周一冲击波的反应，并表示贝莱德的 2025 年展望保持不变，重点关注美国和“其他地区”。她补充说，“对美国也有结构性需求。”马尔基奥尼在彭博电视上发表讲话时还就美联储和欧洲央行可能降息的预期发表了评论。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-29/blackrock-focus-on-us-equities-selectivity-elsewhere-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 10:05:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰称一周内袭击了俄罗斯第二座大型炼油厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/ukraine-says-it-hit-second-major-russian-oil-refinery-in-a-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰一夜之间对俄罗斯九个地区发动了最大规模的无人机袭击之一，一周内第二座大型炼油厂遭袭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/ukraine-says-it-hit-second-major-russian-oil-refinery-in-a-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 09:41:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟最严格的 ESG 基金类别遭遇史上最严重赎回</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/eu-s-greenest-funds-see-biggest-outflows-ever-in-bull-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者放弃了受到低迷回报、监管疲劳和政治反弹困扰的策略，符合欧盟最严格 ESG 标准的基金上个季度遭遇了创纪录的资金流出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/eu-s-greenest-funds-see-biggest-outflows-ever-in-bull-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 08:27:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙经济延续新冠疫情后增长势头，增长 0.8%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/spain-s-economy-extends-post-covid-streak-with-0-8-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙经济是欧元区最大成员国中表现最好的国家，去年年底强劲增长，延续了 2020 年疫情封锁结束后开始的增长势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/spain-s-economy-extends-post-covid-streak-with-0-8-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员押注欧洲央行将需要进一步深化和加速降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/traders-bet-ecb-will-need-to-deepen-and-accelerate-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员押注，由于美国关税风险和该地区的政治动荡给欧盟经济带来压力，欧洲央行将不得不采取更积极的降息方式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/traders-bet-ecb-will-need-to-deepen-and-accelerate-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价下跌，因交易商关注特朗普关税影响和库存</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/oil-holds-biggest-gain-in-two-weeks-as-tariff-threats-dominate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商权衡唐纳德特朗普计划对美国主要原油供应国加拿大和其他国家征收关税的潜在后果以及库存前景，油价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/oil-holds-biggest-gain-in-two-weeks-as-tariff-threats-dominate</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 23:21:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
